Job-Specific AI Resume Optimizer

Job-Specific AI Resume Optimizer is a web application that helps candidates apply smarter using AI. Users can create jobs directly in the system or capture job details via a LinkedIn browser extension. With a single click on Apply, the AI optimizes the user’s CV for the specific role, making it ATS-friendly, generates a professional job-specific email, creates a polished PDF of the optimized CV, and sends it directly to the recruiter. The platform transforms standard CVs into role-specific resumes, helping candidates improve visibility and increase interview chances with minimal effort.
